<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lien invalide — SailingLoc</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7f1d1d 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }
        .brand {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        .card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 48px 40px 36px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .badge {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: #fee2e2;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 28px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(239,68,68,0.3);
        }
        .badge svg { width: 38px; height: 38px; }
        h1 { color: #111827; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .subtitle { color: #6b7280; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 28px; }
        .info-card {
            background: #fff7f7;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 18px 24px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 28px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        .footer-dot {
            width: 8px; height: 8px;
            background: #fca5a5;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-block;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="brand">⚓ SailingLoc</div>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="badge">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/>
                <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h1>Lien invalide ou expiré</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Ce lien de confirmation n'est pas valide<br>ou a déjà été utilisé.</p>
        <div class="info-card">
            <strong>Que faire ?</strong><br>
            Si vous venez de créer votre compte, vérifiez votre boîte mail et utilisez le lien le plus récent reçu de SailingLoc.<br><br>
            Si le problème persiste, contactez le support à <strong>support@sailingloc.fr</strong>.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <span class="footer-dot"></span>
        &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} SailingLoc — Tous droits réservés
    </div>
</body>
</html>
